text: Dr. Calvin is kind and patient with great personality. Dr. Calvin is very professional and knowledgeable. We visited his clinic in Ferrer hospital and it was excellent.

Recently, I had my colonoscopy surgery performed by Dr Frances Sheau. She agreed with my request to give lighter Anaesthesia on me. It was indicated on her surgical notes. During the surgery, she forgot and gave full dosages. Quite disappointed.

During the post review session, she explained she did not like the idea and decided differently. I was awake during the surgery but not consulted.
